## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the scope of publicly accessible information. Some sources may not reflect the most current developments in counterterrorism strategies. Additionally, the effectiveness of counterterrorism measures can vary significantly across different regions and contexts, which may not be fully captured in this report.

